  <div class="head">
    <h1><span class="cfg" id="cfgprefix">~/.claude/</span>config</h1>
    <span class="spring"></span>
    <button class="small" id="themebtn" title="toggle light/dark theme">◐ theme</button>
  </div>
  <p class="sub">Skills, commands, agents, and config files — versioned here, symlinked into the Claude config dir. Collections (like <b>work/</b>, gitignored) mirror the same shape and merge in automatically. Everything is plain files: review &amp; commit with git — or use the git panel below. <b>Ctrl/⌘-K</b> opens the command palette.</p>
  <details id="links">
    <summary>links <span id="linksum"></span></summary>
    <div id="linkrows"></div>
    <div class="cfgdir" id="cfgrow"></div>
    <div class="cfgdir hint" id="cfghint"></div>
